@node "rict" "Ricardo Rosset"

Ricardo Rosset
==============

This Season-

Wins:			0
Pole Positions:		0
Fastest Laps:		0
Best Race Pos:		8th

Total Number of Wins:	0
Career Best Race Pos:	8th
Championships:		0

Rosset had a good strediy season, learning the ropes. He put in some
solid drives, not making any sily moves or many mistakes. It's obvious
from this season that Rosset's unlikely to be a super star, but with a
season of expierence behind him, he is likley to grow into an extremly
competant driver.

@endnode
