@node "pedy" "Pedro Lamy"

Pedro Lamy
==========

This Season-

Wins:			0
Pole Positions:		0
Fastest Laps:		0
Best Race Pos:		9th

Total Number of Wins:	0
Career Best Race Pos:	6th
Championships:		0

No one realy knows exactly how quick Lamy is. He has had a good
pedigree in juniour formulas - finishing second in the International
Formaula 3000 Championship and winning the Formula Opel Euroseris.
Despite showing well against Luca Badoer last year, this year Lamy has
struggled against his team mates (with the exception of Itailian pay
driver Giovanni Lavaggi); he only just fought off new boy Tarso Marques
and other new commer Giancarlo Fisichella beat him hands down.

@endnode
@node "giaa" "Giancarlo Fisichella"

Giancarlo Fisichella
====================

This Season-

Wins:			0
Pole Positions:		0
Fastest Laps:		0
Best Race Pos:		8th

Total Number of Wins:	0
Career Best Race Pos:	8th
Championships:		0

Fisichella made an extremly impressive debut this season, fighting off
the attentions of the highly talented Lamy. He was so impressive that
Benetton given him a teast drive; in which he was only a few tenths
of a second slower than the regualar drivers. Despite his obvious
talent, he was dropped during the middle of the season due to lack of
budget.

@endnode
