Only did a couple of races at the start of the season and
carried his reputation from F3000 with him; fast but erratic.
At his debut in Brazil he crashed out in the rain and in Argentina 
he ran into the back of Martin Brundle.

@endnode
@node "gioi" "Giovanni Lavaggi"

This Season-

Wins:			0
Pole Positions:		0
Fastest Laps:		0
Best Race Pos:		10th

Total Number of Wins:	0
Career Best Race Pos:	10th
Championships:		0

Was brought in from the German Grand Prix onwards to bring some money
to Minardi. He failed to quallify three times out of the 6 times he
competed, and the other times he quallified last. He did however prove
himself to be a sensible driver as (most of the time) he let the front
runners past and made few mistakes.

@endnode
