Freq'ing Racing Speed
---------------------

Use the following format:

RSPEED_IS#.LHA


Replace # with the issue No. you require e.g. - To get the first 
issue of Racing Speed:

RSPEED_IS1.LHA

-----------------------------

The next issue of Racing Speed is due out early March. Every issue
release will be announced in the following echos:

NEWS_AMY          (Amiganet)
ANNOUNCE_AMY      (Amiganet)
AMINFO            (Amnet)

